==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undecylenic
<hw>Un*dec`y*len"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or designating, an acid <chform>C11H20O2</chform>,
homologous with acrylic acid, and obtained as a white crystalline
substance by the distillation of castor oil.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undecylic</ent>⟦br⟧
